display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (A\times  B\right )\mathclose {}}\colon  A\mathbin {\nrightarrow } B]]></fr:tex>, also called the <fr:em><fr:strong>total <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-00I7.xml"
addr="jms-00I7"
title="Relation">relation</fr:link></fr:strong></fr:em>, so that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a\mathrel {{\mathopen {}\left (A\times  B\right )\mathclose {}}}b]]></fr:tex> for all <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[b\in  B]]></fr:tex>. In other words, <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (A\times  B\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> is the <fr:em>total</fr:em> subset of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A\times  B]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
